 details regarding this change and contact research@feedingamerica.org for guidance on comparisons over time.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           & https://www.feedingamerica.org/research/map-the-meal-gap/how-we-got-the-map-data   &  &  & \\\\\n\t Notes on Estimates of Food Insecurity by Race and Ethnicity                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       